OL,3,CFresh plans to create holiday let and
OL,4,Ccafe at old Nude Dunes site
OL,6,FFresh proposals have been put forward
OL,7,Fto convert Jersey's former Nude Dunes
OL,8,Fbeachfront restaurant at La Pulente
OL,9,Finto a self-catered holiday let and a
OL,10,Fcafe.
OL,12,FOwner Nadia Millar appeared to admit
OL,13,Fdefeat in December after years of
OL,14,Fprotests and pushbacks from planning
OL,15,Fsince the eatery ceased trading in
OL,16,Flate 2023, as officials and local
OL,17,Fresidents disagreed with her desire to
OL,18,Foffer accommodation.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
