OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1778220034
OL,3,CFresh plans to create holiday let and
OL,4,Ccafe at old Nude Dunes site
OL,6,FShe then agreed to a change in use
OL,7,Fwhich would allow businesses such as a
OL,8,Fbeauty salon and pharmacy, but blocks
OL,9,Fanyone from living there or hot food
OL,10,Fbeing served.
OL,12,FHowever, in the latest twist, Ms
OL,13,FMillar's latest application "to
OL,14,Fprovide a viable business" wants guest
OL,15,Fstays back on the table, alongside a
OL,16,Fsmaller cafe and a public toilet.
OL,18,FThe plans add: "The aim is to provide
OL,19,Funique self-catering holiday
OL,20,Faccommodation with fantastic views
OL,21,Facross St Ouen's Bay.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
