FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1778220034
OL,3,CFresh plans to create holiday let and
OL,4,Ccafe at old Nude Dunes site
OL,6,F"A scaled-down cafe would remain on
OL,7,Fthe site, focusing on being a "beach
OL,8,Fcafe" where customers can sit on the
OL,9,Fexisting terrace at the north of the
OL,10,Fpremises, or take food and drink away."
OL,12,FThe holiday let would include two
OL,13,Fbedrooms, a living room and kitchen, a
OL,14,Fbathroom and an office, plus private
OL,15,Foutdoor space on the south terrace.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
