FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1778220034
OL,3,CFresh plans to create holiday let and
OL,4,Ccafe at old Nude Dunes site
OL,6,FThe plans say these changes would
OL,7,Fboost the local economy and ease
OL,8,Fpressure on existing tourist hotspots,
OL,9,Fas well as offering visitors "greater
OL,10,Fflexibility and privacy compared to
OL,11,Ftraditional hotels".
OL,13,FIt concludes: "This proposal offers a
OL,14,Fpragmatic and sustainable solution to
OL,15,Fthe underutilisation of a key site."
OL,17,FHowever, there is likely to be
OL,18,Fsignificant public opposition.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
