PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1778220034
OL,3,CFresh plans to create holiday let and
OL,4,Ccafe at old Nude Dunes site
OL,6,FThe building in St Brelade sits within
OL,7,Fthe Coastal National Park and hundreds
OL,8,Fof people lined up along the
OL,9,Fbeachfront in summer 2024 to protest
OL,10,Fagainst allowing accommodation - with
OL,11,Fconcerns it could lead to further
OL,12,Fprivatisation of the coastline.
OL,14,FThe plans were published on Tuesday 5
OL,15,FMay and no decision date has been set.
OL,17,FNude Dunes: A timeline of events
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
